    "href": "https://www.ifixit.com/Guide/Steam+Deck+Action+Buttons+(ABXY)+Replacement/148950"
  }, "aforementioned iFixit guide"), ". I attached the buttons to their spots on the keyed bottom plate of the mold box with some thin, rolled clay wormy\ndealies and then thoroughly cleaned them with some q-tips and isopropyl alcohol. It is important to be ", mdx("em", {
