  })), mdx("p", null, "Another 5h later I carefully demolded my two part mold. I once again removed tape, rubber bands and the top brace, pulling out\nthe toothpick halves in the process. I then carefully pulled the two halves of the box apart again and equally carefully peeled\nthe two parts of the mold apart from each other.", mdx("sup", {
